This allows multiple iPhone devices to connect over Wifi+Bluetooth.
One device acts as host and others are guests. Host can play song which
is streamed to all the guests and play in them too. Though the
synchronization is not perfect but one can work on it.

I used this loader :
https://github.com/jonathantribouharet/JTMaterialSpinner The
Peer-to-Peer connection, streaming and stream-player is based on:
https://github.com/tonyd256/TDAudioPlayer &
https://github.com/tonyd256/TDAudioStreamer
